 more importantly, why my father took so much pride in helping people. So I opened my own agency at the age of 21 in November, 1999. Today, my agency has been ranked in the top 3% in the nation with Farmers Insurance more than once (Championship Award Winner). And I take pride in what I do. I want be one of the best agents in Texas!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-21 17:17:25', '2014-03-21 17:17:25', '', 18, 'http://jimenez.net16.net/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
