rcent of Midwestern homeowners had a flood insurance policy in 2011 along with 12 percent of homeowners in the West and 5 percent in the Northeast.', 'Flood', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '424-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-29 11:18:15', '2014-03-29 11:18:15', '', 424, 'http://jimenez.net16.net/424-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
